Remarks: The Emerald Cory Catfish is a very hardy and resilient fish.  Disease should not be a concern provided that you maintain the aquarium to standards.

Common name: Peppered corydoras, salt and pepper catfish

Remarks: A very peaceful species, that does not make an ideal community fish due to its small adult size. It is easily intimidated by larger tank mates and will not compete well with them for food.

Common name: Threestripe corydoras, leopard catfish, false julii cory
